Download Data from a Panel

Use this task to download data in the form of a CSV file from a PW EMS Monitoring and Reporting Panel.

  1. In the navigation bar, select the Dashboard icon .
  2. From the Dashboard pop-up menu, click Manage.
  3. In the Dashboards window that displays, select any existing dashboard that you want to extract data from one of its panels. For example: ClickHouse Performance Monitor.
  4. When the dashboard displays, click the arrow at the top of the panel that you want to extract data from and select Inspect > Data. For example, the following panel is from the ClickHouse Performance Monitor Part Info Base panel:
  5. In the Inspect dialog box that displays the Data tab, click Download CSV
    The .CSV file is saved automatically to your Web browser default download location. For example: Part Info Base-data-2021-05-12 16_04_29
